text: Luigi Cangiullo (1897 - 1 September 1930) was an Italian diver. He competed at the 1924 Summer Olympics and the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1897 births Category:1930 deaths Category:Italian male divers Category:Olympic divers of Italy Category:Divers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Divers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Naples
